Map knife, Bulls Arena.
The Bullfighters and Terrorists are fighting knife and cover against the Bulls Counter-Terrorists.
Terrorists have to play together in the middle of the arena to win against the Bulls.
The Counter-Terrorists have to kill all the terrorists before time runs out to win.
